reviewText: The Main Character's acting was actually very good, frankly, it is amazing that the sidekick character's total lack of any acting ability didn't throw him off. The project was laid to ruin the moment the sidekick entered the picture.
Plays like a terrible 80's sitcom. If you want something to laugh at, this is for you!
This did not grab my attention and we only watched about 20 minutes of it before deciding not to finish it.
good, well done, but no sub-titles
Everything went very well with this purchase
